sun <sun> raises crude postings 50 cts
    new york, march 12 - 
sun co said it raised the contract price it will pay for crude oil 50
cts a barrel, effective today. the increase brings sun's posted price
for the west texas intermediate and west texas sour grades to 17.50
dlrs/bbl. the light louisiana sweet grade was also raised 50 cts to
17.85 dlrs/bbl. sun co last changed its crude postings on march 4.
